{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"968-i-can-help","title":"I Can Help!","description":"A big girl or boy can help others in many ways. Helping is so much fun! This book is one of the four books in the 'Growing Up' series.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mini Shrinivasan"],"illustrators":["Aman Randhawa"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/968-i-can-help"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/705491/size3/f2ecd62b4dc76be8fa891bf361c2b379.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/705491/size6/f2ecd62b4dc76be8fa891bf361c2b379.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11785/size6/4ad71862580823a59ed0c0d7217f09db.jpg","text":"I am a big girl.\nI can help other people.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11786/size6/931658dfc2af19dffd75a5efcfad837a.jpg","text":"After school, I like to feed my brother.\nHe loves it.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11787/size6/1f8df97945778fe121a6dbf643c633be.jpg","text":"When I have a holiday,\nI help my mother to get ready to go to the office.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11788/size6/23daac69d7f87dd7536c0ef20bdf0479.jpg","text":"In the evening, I help my father in his shop.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11789/size6/06da2479be8bc41ae072733c5504bad9.jpg","text":"But sometimes my mother says, “Please, do not help me!”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11790/size6/925563521b6b9efc9ec9f5c3b7c08cc3.jpg","text":"And sometimes my father says,\n“Thank you, but please do not help me today.”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11791/size6/fb23b71932102991183e1d9532d917e4.jpg","text":"Sometimes they both tell me to sit in one place.\nI like to read a book then!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11792/size6/830c5b9610bb8b7fdc6ddce60dfd9912.jpg","text":"I like to help my grandmother.\nShe tells me stories.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11793/size6/4b945f4e2c9aac7fe51a017388e7c556.jpg","text":"My brother is still small.\nHe cannot help at all.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11794/size6/9cc9864d68d003c20c69c01f95fbfdaa.jpg","text":"But I am a big girl.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11795/size6/6edb9a072b327b1e60218a901c63154c.jpg","text":"I can help other people.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":120}}